survey_response.review_text: I recently had a wisdom teeth extraction procedure done by Dr. Fahad and I am pleased with the level of care I received. From the initial consultation to the post-operative follow-up, Dr. Fahad and their team made me feel comfortable and well-informed throughout the entire process. During the procedure, Dr. Fahad was efficient and skilled, making the experience as painless as possible. I also found the clinic equipment and hygiene very well maintained. Dr. Fahad also took the time to explain the procedure and answer any questions I had, which helped me clear any concerns I had before the surgery. The recovery period was also relatively smooth, and I appreciated the clear and detailed instructions provided by him. Overall, I recommend the Dental Expertz clinic for anyone in need of wisdom teeth extraction. Their professionalism, expertise, and caring demeanor made what could have been a stressful experience a relatively easy one.

Dr. Fahad believes in the right to information act where the patient deserves to know what materials are being used, and then allows the patient to choose the treatment accordingly. 

The clinic is clean and the tools used are always being upgraded. 

Very happy and definitely recommended to be treated by Dr. Fahad.
